content.raw: Could we keep the version requirements that were reverted in d5fac79? This PR uses API introduced on those versions, so `ign-gazebo` won't compile against a lower version of those dependencies. It's best if we let the user know at configuration time, than having them figure it out when the compilation stops halfway.
